CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,FA university lecturer who suffers with
OL,7,Farthritis says she faces a "never-
OL,8,Fending" struggle after being told she
OL,9,Fneeds to lose 7st before being
OL,10,Fconsidered for knee surgery.
OL,12,FDr Claire Speck, a biology lecturer at
OL,13,FYork University who lives in North
OL,14,FNewbald near Hull, needs a knee
OL,15,Freplacement after suffering pain for
OL,16,Fmore than nine years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,FBut one local health trust told the 60-
OL,7,Fyear-old, who weighs 140kg (22st), she
OL,8,Fmust lose almost a third of her
OL,9,Fbodyweight before she can even be
OL,10,Fadded to the waiting list for an
OL,11,Foperation.
OL,13,FAnother said she must drastically
OL,14,Freduce her body mass index (BMI).
OL,16,FShe said: "It's this never-ending
OL,17,Fsituation of doors being slammed in my
OL,18,Fface. Weight loss is not an easy thing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,F"I know lots of people think it is
OL,7,Freally easy, but the more that I can't
OL,8,Fexercise, the more I struggle, because
OL,9,Fone of my ways of losing weight is by
OL,10,Fexercise."
OL,12,FDr Speck, who uses a walking stick,
OL,13,Fsays she has been trying to shed
OL,14,Fweight since the coronavirus lockdown
OL,15,Fwithout success.
OL,17,FShe has tried physiotherapy, but says
OL,18,Fexercising exacerbates her pain.
OL,20,FShe had to stop using weight loss
OL,21,Finjections due to "complications".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,F"My quality of life has really
OL,7,Fchanged," she said.
OL,9,F"I can't do things that I used to do -
OL,10,FI can't take the dogs for a walk, I
OL,11,Fcan take them up to the park or the
OL,12,Ffield but that's about as far as it
OL,13,Fgoes.
OL,15,F"I have a granddaughter who's two and
OL,16,Fa bit and I can't play around on the
OL,17,Ffloor with her because I can't be on
OL,18,Fmy knees - how on earth do I get up
OL,19,Foff the floor once I'm down there?"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,FThe National Institute for Clinical
OL,7,FExcellence (NICE) says a person's BMI
OL,8,F- a measure based on their weight and
OL,9,Fheight - should not be the sole
OL,10,Fconsideration when assessing whether
OL,11,Fthey are eligible for surgery.
OL,13,FZoe Chivers, of Arthritis UK, said:
OL,14,F"Waiting lists across England are
OL,15,Fincredibly large - there's about
OL,16,F800,000 people sitting on those
OL,17,Fwaiting lists at the moment - and
OL,18,Fthose people who have increased BMIs
OL,19,Fare not being put on the waiting lists
OL,20,Fand that is absolutely abhorrent.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,F"People who would benefit from life
OL,7,Fchanging surgery, such as knee
OL,8,Freplacements and hip replacements are
OL,9,Factually those who would gain the most
OL,10,Ffrom having these surgeries in terms
OL,11,Fof getting their life back."
OL,13,FA spokesperson for York and
OL,14,FScarborough Teaching Hospitals NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust, which told Dr Speck
OL,16,Fshe needed to lose 7st, said:
OL,17,F"Decisions about whether a patient is
OL,18,Fadded to a surgical waiting list are
OL,19,Fmade by clinicians based on national
OL,20,Fguidance, clinical evidence, and an
OL,21,Findividual assessment of risk.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,F"For some procedures, being
OL,7,Fsignificantly overweight can increase
OL,8,Fthe risk of complications during and
OL,9,Fafter surgery, including problems with
OL,10,Fanaesthetic, wound healing, infection,
OL,11,Fand recovery. Where this is the case,
OL,12,Fpatients may be supported to improve
OL,13,Ftheir health before surgery to help
OL,14,Fensure treatment is as safe and
OL,15,Feffective as possible.
OL,17,F"These decisions are made on a case-by-
OL,18,Fcase basis, and patients continue to
OL,19,Freceive clinical support and advice,
OL,20,Fincluding other services where
OL,21,Fappropriate."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1778868675
OL,3,CLecturer denied knee surgery until she
OL,4,Closes 7st
OL,6,FThe Humber and North Yorkshire Health
OL,7,Fand Care Partnership said a BMI of
OL,8,Fmore than 40 carried "additional risks
OL,9,Fof infection, complications with
OL,10,Fanaesthesia, and blood clots".
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "Surgery is not
OL,13,Fruled out solely on the basis of a
OL,14,Fpatient's BMI. Each patient is
OL,15,Findividually assessed to determine the
OL,16,Fbest course of treatment for them,
OL,17,Fbalancing the risks associated with
OL,18,Fsurgery with their individual
OL,19,Fcircumstances."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
